---
// UpgradeHero — hero for the Square upgrade ads landing page.
// Headline puts the buyer outcome up front ("the website your customers
// actually see"). Single primary CTA -> #apply. Trust strip baked in
// directly under the CTA so cold ad traffic gets credibility above the fold.
---
<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<section id="top" class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-line">
  <div class="grid-bg absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-60" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="accent-glow absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-[640px] h-[640px] z-0" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-8 pt-10 sm:pt-16 pb-20 sm:pb-24">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- LEFT: copy -->
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Square Website Upgrade</span>

        <h1 class="mt-5 text-[2.3rem] sm:text-[3rem] lg:text-[3.4rem] leading-[1.04] font-bold text-text">
          Keep Square. Upgrade the
          <span class="text-accent">Website Your Customers Actually See.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 max-w-[60ch] text-[1.05rem] sm:text-[1.12rem] leading-[1.6] text-text-soft">
          You already use Square for
          <span class="text-text font-medium">booking</span>,
          <span class="text-text font-medium">payments</span>,
          <span class="text-text font-medium">staff schedules</span>, and
          <span class="text-text font-medium">customer records</span>.
          We build the premium website around it — so your shop looks better, books smoother, and feels like your brand from the first tap.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-5 gap-y-3">
          <a href="#apply" data-hero-cta class="btn-primary">
            Get My Free 10-Minute Website Review
            <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-4 max-w-[58ch] text-[0.95rem] text-text-soft leading-relaxed">
          I'll send back 3 specific ways to make your current site look more premium and easier to book from. No hard pitch.
        </p>

        <!-- Trust strip -->
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-2 text-[0.85rem] text-text-muted">
          <span class="font-display font-semibold text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Featured builds</span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline text-line-2" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span class="text-text-soft">Modern Classic Barbershop</span>
          <span class="text-line-2" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span class="text-text-soft">Fitchin Auto Detail &amp; Tint</span>
          <span class="text-line-2" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span class="text-text-soft">All Transport Bus Co.</span>
          <span class="text-line-2" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted">Built in Zanesville, OH</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: Modern Classic mobile screenshot -->
      <div class="relative" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-[320px] sm:max-w-[340px]">
          <div class="absolute -inset-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/30 via-accent/5 to-transparent rounded-[2rem] blur-3xl opacity-60" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="relative aspect-[9/19] rounded-[1.6rem] overflow-hidden border border-accent/40 shadow-[0_30px_80px_-20px_rgba(255,107,26,0.5)] bg-surface-2 rotate-[-2deg]">
            <img
              src="/showcase/modern-classic-mobile.png"
              alt="Modern Classic Barbershop — a custom Square-powered website built by Designed to Elevate"
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
              width="1320"
              height="2678"
              loading="eager"
              decoding="async"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Live pill overlay -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent px-3 py-1.5 font-display text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-bg shadow-[0_8px_24px_-8px_rgba(255,107,26,0.7)]">
            <span class="relative flex h-1.5 w-1.5" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="absolute inline-flex h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-bg/60 animate-ping"></span>
              <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-1.5 w-1.5 bg-bg"></span>
            </span>
            Live on Square
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- /HERO SECTION -->
